    "The results indicate significant differences in thematic focus and lexical choices between ChatGPT-3.5-generated and human-produced academic writing.",
    "However, the study has limitations.",
    "Despite the significant patterns of variation revealed across the two corpora, the small size of the corpora could influence the significance of individual wordings discussed in the present study, which may be less significant in larger corpora.",
    "The study encompasses 30 different topics which may influence the selection of lexis and collocation strengths present across the two corpora as well as the selected themes arising.",
    "Future research could compare essays of similar topics so as to determine variation within the same thematic topics."
